    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical reliability and sophisticated design. This unit has been meticulously maintained, ensuring a seamless driving experience and a well-preserved aesthetic. Rigorously inspected to meet our professional standards, it offers a superior balance of performance and long-term value. We invite discerning buyers to acquire this exceptional example of engineering excellence.",
      "price": 34800.0,
