      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in great shape and has been well-loved, showing just a bit of character from the road but still running like a total champ. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a dependable, comfy drive without the brand-new price tag. Come say hi and take it for a test drive\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
